OL,3,C'Destroy ninja swords' say police as
OL,4,C66 handed in just last month
OL,6,FSixty six banned 'ninja swords' have
OL,7,Fbeen handed to police across West
OL,8,FYorkshire.
OL,10,FA recent weapons amnesty by West
OL,11,FYorkshire Police saw a total of 81
OL,12,Fbladed weapons given to the force over
OL,13,Fthe last month.
OL,15,FThe Home Office scheme came ahead of a
OL,16,Fnew law making it a criminal offence
OL,17,Fto possess ninja swords in private or
OL,18,Fmanufacture, import, or sell them.
OL,20,FIt came into effect on August 1.
