OL,3,C'Destroy ninja swords' say police as
OL,4,C66 handed in just last month
OL,6,F"As a force, we of course support any
OL,7,Fmeasure which increases public safety
OL,8,Fand which can help us get dangerous
OL,9,Fweapons that can cause serious harm
OL,10,Foff our streets."
OL,12,FThe force said it is continuing to
OL,13,Fmonitor stores and dealers who
OL,14,Fpreviously sold ninja swords to make
OL,15,Fsure they are complying with the law.
